\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
Obs/pr The average number of times each pair was observed.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
Entropy The total entropy of these pairs in this dataset, as defined previously:
 for word-pairs 
\begin_inset Formula $(w_{L},w_{R})$
\end_inset

 it is 
\begin_inset Formula $H=-\sum_{w_{L},w_{R}}p(w_{L},w_{R})\log_{2}p(w_{L},w_{R})$
