 are not normally considered to be body parts, but are, in some sense, deeply,
 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

parts of oneself
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

.
 Similarly, 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

